        What to Expect When Selling in Hawthorne
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Hawthorne attracts a competitive buyer pool and rewards well-prepared campaigns. Here's what local sellers should understand before they list.
      </p>
